---
title: Meatloaf à la Mom with Potato Wedges, Broccoli & Gravy
description: Everyone agrees that no one makes meatloaf quite like Mom. But our chefs will settle for the next best thing by taking a page from her cookbook and passing on this recipe. The meal stays as true to tradition as can be: Ground beef mini loaves are brushed with a ketchup glaze, served with roasted broccoli and potatoes, and drizzled with an herby gravy. And if you’d like to claim this recipe as your own, don’t worry—mum’s the word.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63ec07995b8e65c41d0748a9-6f06c284.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/654a9afa33e8a37769159aac.pdf
time required: 45 minutes
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/meatloaf-a-la-mom-654a9afa33e8a37769159aac
nutrition:
  calories: 670 kcal
  fat: 37 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
